  "description": "A coastal scene featuring choppy, grey-blue water crashing against a rocky shoreline. The foreground is dominated by dark, wet rocks, partially submerged by the waves. Beyond the rocks, the ocean extends into the distance, with visible waves and white foam. A hazy cityscape is discernible on the horizon, seemingly shrouded in fog or mist. The sky is pale and overcast, contributing to a muted color palette. The overall composition focuses on the interplay between the rough textures of the rocks and the dynamic movement of the sea.",
